plivo-android-examples folder should be present in this directory.
It should contain PlivoOutbound, PlivoInbound and PlivoPhone sample apps.
android_ndk_r9 path, sample android-app path and swig path should be given in the environment variable.
Gradle should be installed in the system.

Build
----
$ make build_pjsip 
# this will displpay a set of comments, from those choose a function
# to build pjsip for the required architecture
#set pjproject-2.2.1 path in the environment variable

$ make all
# builds the jni and the gradle

$make release
# builds the jni and the gradle without having any backend logs